ccre.ctrl

Class CommunicationFailureExtendedMotor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.ctrl.ExtendedMotor
      • ccre.ctrl.CommunicationFailureExtendedMotor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FloatOutput

    public class CommunicationFailureExtendedMotor
extends ExtendedMotor
implements FloatOutput
    A fake implementation of ExtendedMotor that is suitable for use when communications could not be established initially with the device. This will provide lots of stubbed-out functionality and will log warning messages whenever it is interacted with.
    Author:
    skeggsc
